<blockquote><p>Remember to have a life, remember you can say no, and remember to ask for help.</p></blockquote>
<p>Thanks Mika for all you do to help make WordPress better. Be sure to check out her <a href="http://halfelf.org/ebooks/">eBooks</a> if you&#8217;re looking for help on using WordPress Multisite. </p>
