<p><a href="http://emptynestthemes.com/2012/12/10/color-block-wordpress-website-theme/"><strong>Color Block</strong></a> is a responsive, clean, colorful and very readable theme.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone  wp-image-12337" title="screenshot" src="http://i2.wp.com/weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/screenshot1-150x150.png?w=150" alt="" /></p>
<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/epublishing"><strong>ePublishing</strong></a> is a simple theme with a cool sticky post design and nice typography.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone  wp-image-12338" title="screenshot-1" src="http://i2.wp.com/weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/screenshot-11-150x150.png?w=150" alt="" /></p>
