igned for artists. Cheer a whimsical and textured holiday theme. Curiosity is a simple, clean, and elegant theme. Embed is a simple and elegant one coloumn Twenty Twelve child theme. Mimbolove is a simple and customizable theme with support for a custom menu, header image, two column layout, and a footer sidebar. [&hellip;]''>Weblog Tools Collection: WordPress Theme Releases for 12/24</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
